HEADWORD: Paracelsian
<hw>Par`a*cel"si*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <def>Of,
pertaining to, or in conformity with, the practice of
<etsep>Paracelsus</etsep>, a Swiss physician and alchemist of the 15th
century.</def> <rj><au>Ferrand.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Paracelsian</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Paracelsian
<hw>Par`a*cel"si*an</hw>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A follower of
<persfn>Paracelsus</persfn> or his practice or teachings.</def>
<rj><au>Hakewill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

